    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Women's scarves of some light fabric, often white and sheer, draped around the neck and shoulders and tied in a knot with ends hanging loosely.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
